OL,5,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FDuring the week's final visit, to
OL,7,     FJames and Neil's Uplawmoor Hotel
OL,8,     Fnear Glasgow, the B&Bers try their
OL,9,     Fhands at curling. But some
OL,10,     Frelationships seem to be on thin
OL,11,     Fice.
OL,12,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's been a topsy-turvy week with
OL,14,     Fsome B&Bers delighted with their
OL,15,     Fscores - and others not so much.
OL,16,     FAfter a little bit of a praise and
OL,17,     Fa lot of moaning, who'll win?
